3. src/app/api/search/route.ts
================================================================================

Lines 8-23: Async Rate Limiting with Fingerprinting
  OLD:  const { success, remaining } = rateLimit(ip, 30, 60000);
  NEW:  const { success, remaining, resetAt } = await rateLimit(
          ip, 30, 60000, "/api/search",
          userAgent, acceptLanguage
        );

ADDED: Extract headers for fingerprinting
  const userAgent = request.headers.get("user-agent");
  const acceptLanguage = request.headers.get("accept-language");

UPDATED: Rate limit failure response with resetAt header
  if (resetAt) {
    response.headers.set("X-RateLimit-Reset", String(Math.ceil(resetAt / 1000)));
  }

Lines 38-41: Include resetAt in success response
  Added X-RateLimit-Reset header with calculated reset time

RESULT: Better rate limit information for clients, fingerprinting enabled

